description: Run builds, tests, and tooling in the terminal—never delegate to the user
alwaysApply: true
---

# Run commands yourself

After making code changes, **run the needed terminal commands yourself** (install, build, test, lint, `cap sync`, etc.). **Do not** end with “please run X” or “you should run Y” unless the environment truly cannot perform the action.

If a command fails, try alternatives or report the error—do not hand off the command to the user as the default outcome.
